10#ifndef OSSL_TEST_ECDSATEST_H
11# define OSSL_TEST_ECDSATEST_H
12
13/*-
14 * NIST CAVP ECDSA KATs:
15 * https://csrc.nist.gov/CSRC/media/Projects/Cryptographic-Algorithm-Validation-Program/documents/dss/186-3ecdsatestvectors.zip
16 *
17 * sha256sum e0d9bee3f760ca3fabb82bd43dd04c13ee64ca9e0b719c6ea64fd52c9f0dd929
18 * 720 KATs from the SigGen.txt file.
19 *
20 * There are also 4 X9.62 KATs; two for prime fields and two for binary fields.
21 */
22
23typedef struct {
24 const int nid; /* curve NID */
25 const int md_nid; /* hash function NID */
26 const char *msg; /* message to sign */
27 const char *d; /* ECDSA private key */
28 const char *Q; /* ECDSA public key: Q = dG */
29 const char *k; /* ECDSA nonce */
30 const char *r; /* ECDSA signature (r,s) */
31 const char *s;
32} ecdsa_cavs_kat_t;
